items.title: PM Modi's Commitment to Tamil Nadu's Growth
items.author: Narendra Modi
items.summary:
- PM Modi emphasized the *Centre's commitment* to the development of *Tamil Nadu* during his speech in Thoothukudi. 
- He reiterated several initiatives aimed at boosting *economic growth* and improving *infrastructure* in the state. 
- Modi's address highlights the ongoing collaboration between the *central government* and *state administration* for the welfare of Tamil Nadu citizens.
